      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 power unit with its signature 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive double-VANOS service. The drivetrain consists of a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. Recent maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul. The suspension is sorted with refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers, preserving the communicative steering geometry. A mechanically sound example ready for spirited apex-hunting.",
