      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-loved daily driver that remains in impressive condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips and light surface marks typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free; the upholstery shows only minimal softening on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all electronic components\u2014from the infotainment system to the climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with recent attention given to the braking system and a fresh oil change. It tracks straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle perfect for someone seeking quality and longevity without the 'new car' price tag.",
